{
  "page": "Master",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b>Master</b> is a noble rank in the <a href=\"/index.php/North\" title=\"North\">North</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Iron_Islands\" title=\"Iron Islands\">Iron Islands</a>, where the institution of <a href=\"/index.php/Knight\" title=\"Knight\">knighthood</a> has virtually no presence. Masters are ranked below <a href=\"/index.php/Lord\" title=\"Lord\">lords</a> and are equivalent to <a href=\"/index.php/Southron\" title=\"Southron\">southron</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Landed_knight\" title=\"Landed knight\">landed knights</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_examples\">Known examples</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known examples\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\"><img alt=\"House Glover.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/20px-House_Glover.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/30px-House_Glover.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/41/House_Glover.svg/40px-House_Glover.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Glover\" title=\"House Glover\">House Glover</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_Deepwood_Motte\" title=\"Master of Deepwood Motte\">Masters of Deepwood Motte</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall\" title=\"House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg/20px-House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d2/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg/30px-House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d2/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg/40px-House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harlaw_Hall\" title=\"House Harlaw of Harlaw Hall\">House Harlaw</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_Harlaw_Hall\" title=\"Master of Harlaw Hall\">Masters of Harlaw Hall</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill\" title=\"House Harlaw of Harridan Hill\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw of Harridan Hill.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/4/43/House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill.svg/20px-House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/4/43/House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill.svg/30px-House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/4/43/House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill.svg/40px-House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Harridan_Hill\" title=\"House Harlaw of Harridan Hill\">House Harlaw</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_Harridan_Hill\" title=\"Master of Harridan Hill\">Masters of Harridan Hill</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering\" title=\"House Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering\"><img alt=\"House Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering.svg/20px-House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/d0/House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering.svg/30px-House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/d0/House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering.svg/40px-House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering\" title=\"House Harlaw of the Tower of Glimmering\">House Harlaw</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_the_Tower_of_Glimmering\" title=\"Master of the Tower of Glimmering\">Masters of the Tower of Glimmering</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\"><img alt=\"House Tallhart.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/20px-House_Tallhart.svg.png\" width=\"20\" height=\"22\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/30px-House_Tallhart.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fe/House_Tallhart.svg/40px-House_Tallhart.svg.png 2x\" /></a> <a href=\"/index.php/House_Tallhart\" title=\"House Tallhart\">House Tallhart</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_Torrhen%27s_Square\" title=\"Master of Torrhen&#39;s Square\">Masters of Torrhen's Square</a></li></ul>\n<p>Among the cadet branches of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw\" title=\"House Harlaw\">House Harlaw</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/House_Harlaw_of_Grey_Garden\" title=\"House Harlaw of Grey Garden\">Harlaws of Grey Garden</a> are an exception as the current head, Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Harras_Harlaw\" title=\"Harras Harlaw\">Harras Harlaw</a>, is an actual knight and is thus entitled to the style \"<a href=\"/index.php/Knight_of_Grey_Garden\" title=\"Knight of Grey Garden\">Knight of Grey Garden</a>.\"\n</p><p>Note that some houses in the south use the style \"Master\" as a secondary title (i.e. <a href=\"/index.php/House_Velaryon\" title=\"House Velaryon\">House Velaryon</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Lord_of_the_Tides\" title=\"Lord of the Tides\">Lords of the Tides</a> and <a href=\"/index.php/Master_of_Driftmark\" title=\"Master of Driftmark\">Masters of Driftmark</a>), but this is only a personal preference rather than being indicative of rank.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Master&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a class=\"external text\" href=\"https://asoiaf.westeros.org/index.php?/topic/34958-the-asoiaf-wiki-thread/page/71/#comment-7590729\">Ran, Westeros.org</a>: \"Yes, long ago when we were hashing out this stuff, <a href=\"/index.php/George_R.R._Martin\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"George R.R. Martin\">GRRM</a> indicated that the \"master\" title -- at least in the north - was his way of indicating the equivalent of a landed knightly house, like the way the Templetons are Knights of Sevenstars.<sup><abbr title=\"The preceding text is copied directly from its source and should remain as is. Please do not correct this to &quot;Ninestars.&quot;\">[sic]</abbr></sup>\" May 17, 2016.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260404203951\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.029 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.070 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 109/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 524/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 1172/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 135/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 7/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1005/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.030/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 5.58 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   58.154      1 -total\n 85.82%   49.905      5 Template:Coa\n 13.32%    7.746      1 Template:References\n 10.35%    6.019      1 Template:Sic\n  9.45%    5.498      1 Template:Abbr\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:37627-0!canonical and timestamp 20260404203951 and revision id 316861\n -->\n",
